description:
Prototype: 
Get Me Out Of Here

Development:
30.08-08.09.2017

Tagline:
Use vehicles and help aliens heist squad escape from the bank!

Description:

In this tactical turn-based game you take control over a group of aliens right after causing an alarm on bank heist. Use different vehicles spread across the map, don't get caught and get safely to you space ship. Will you manage to safe the whole crew and take off with all the money?
